description: This family-run fleet of trucks has been roaming the streets of Miami-Dade & Broward Counties since 2007, and serving up all your favorite premium frozen treats, including over 45 of the most delicious products from Good Humor, Popsicle, Klondike, Blue Bunny, and Rich’s. Invite Drake the Dragon along to your next Party, Fundraiser, Corporate or Community Gathering, etc… and with his delightful ice cream, so sweet, he’ll be sure to make your event quite a “COOL TREAT!"
name: Dragon Ice Cream
